claim.claim-text:
1. A rear projection television (PTV) system, comprising: 
a lighted image source for creating an image; 
a planar element for redirecting the created image toward a target plane, wherein the planar element reflects a first plurality of wavelengths of light and transmits a second plurality of wavelengths of light; 
a focusing means; 
an IR receiving element; and 
a target plane for displaying the created image.
